    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment is Accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is offset by the conservative nature of the single-condition test (worst-case static loading), the high specimen count (N=11), and the dual-metric acceptance approach. The assessment team judges that residual uncertainty does not materially affect the regulatory decision.",
